            <title>[LU-19673] increase osp.*.max_rpcs_in_progress</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19673</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;it&apos;s 4096 currently which means we can destroy 4096/5=819 OST objects/second per OST. this way a constant long lasting load producing unlink/setattr can overflow osp llog.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
