                            <comment id="480450" author="paf0186" created="Fri, 5 Dec 2025 15:18:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ohhh, I missed the &quot;per second&quot; part, I see.&#160; Thank you.&#160; That seems very slow for something like this, yeah.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="480448" author="bzzz" created="Fri, 5 Dec 2025 15:13:34 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Why is it 4096/5?  Where does the 5 come from?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;this is default ext4 commit time, we don&apos;t issue new RPCs before the current batch (upto 4K) has been committed and cancelled.&lt;br/&gt;
I&apos;ve also filed &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19672&quot; title=&quot;batch MDS-OST unlink/setattr RPCs&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-19672&quot;&gt;LU-19672&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
